snippet.title: V Prototype - Level 6
snippet.description:
Hello! We are Zero Garden, and this is our first game: V Prototype.

------------------------------------------

If you would like to try this game you can download it for free here: http://www.yoyogames.com/games/158069-v-prototype

Once you've played the game, please consider giving us some feedback in youtube comments, or in the comments section on the game's page.

All feedback is welcome!
